title: Hour 3 - NBA All-Time Greats, Reggie Miller
itunes:title: Hour 3 - NBA All-Time Greats, Reggie Miller
description:
Dan and the Danettes discuss where Steph Curry ranks among the all-time greats and Reggie Miller joins the show to chime in on the debate and break down Golden State's NBA Finals victory.
